{"tid":1846021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 提供免費治療係正常","createTime":"2020-01-27T12:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T13:14:50.000Z","uid":5866,"like":20,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a6bb77508074930d8798a377006d0bd3177217b6","tid":1846021,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:35:34.000Z","msg":"𠵱啲突發又冇藥醫嘅高傳染性病毒政府提供免費治療係正常，外國(如日本)都會噉做<br />\n<br />\n因為如果你要啲人被隔離之餘重要畀錢噉一定冇人會自願去睇醫生<br />\n班潛伏期病患就會好似計時炸彈噉生活喺社區，最後可能造成社區大爆發<br />\n<br />\n所以個問題從來唔係免費治療<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">問題係政府唔封關</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n封關+免費治療 = 可以導埋為數未必多嘅疑似病患入醫院做隔離治療/觀察<br />\n<br />\n免費治療但唔封關 = 病蝗禍<br />\n香港醫療體系好蚛蟈太多，如果香港重係無掩雞籠噉嘅狀態只會令未來蝗國有/怕病嘅人直衝香港，最後全港大爆發<br />\n<br />\n所以問題由始至終只有一個<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係香港要封關呀</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fd42e65489d60bbbf09cd6c163e71be69c4e1500","tid":1846021,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec37fe041ea0bba82e5cc04452266578a3f129e2","tid":1846021,"uid":288304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:38:58.000Z","msg":"封關就正常，唔封關就把撚<br />\n<br />\n以前哩個制度係唔想D中左的人留在市面唔醫，搞到散晒<br />\n因為以前D人唔會為左醫病而偷渡衝關<br />\n<br />\n依家唔同，佢地過關0成本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f2f59014ae703555fad5447a75ed42061ba039","tid":1846021,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d31d8bdcb0ce09c420992da498fdd677b9a972e","tid":1846021,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec37fe041ea0bba82e5cc04452266578a3f129e2","tid":1846021,"uid":288304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:38:58.000Z","msg":"封關就正常，唔封關就把撚<br />\n<br />\n以前哩個制度係唔想D中左的人留在市面唔醫，搞到散晒<br />\n因為以前D人唔會為左醫病而偷渡衝關<br />\n<br />\n依家唔同，佢地過關0成本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:40:47.000Z","msg":"全港大罷工罷到封關啦屌<br />\n到時大爆發就真係工都冇撚得翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b154121bfbbc5a80e4fc87a82a18a79f049edea","tid":1846021,"uid":247003,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:42:22.000Z","msg":"免費無問題，但一定要只係香港人有lor....依家係用緊我地既錢但隨時你有事都輪唔到你！"},{"pid":"59d2c7db35b0af455e2ac0bdf474ccfcc12d2a20","tid":1846021,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:43:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f6d0c1f05d4569589e31e05a0688c40976ecc38","tid":1846021,"uid":317979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bK2fUvS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbK2fUvS.jpg&h=251726c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PCFhopc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPCFhopc.jpg&h=c990dc3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e173a02ed909f37aa68f2d1562b17922dc45333","tid":1846021,"uid":99573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"True"},{"pid":"bb89b4c394cdaf110e1575de79a89ec999e1fc99","tid":1846021,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:44:00.000Z","msg":"有班大劣閪, 免費都唔會睇醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫佢隔離仲會反抗打返你轉頭"},{"pid":"3fd1771b196db27589a4c87d6bc61f64a98f2aa2","tid":1846021,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"樓主on9 拉"},{"pid":"7f1110e6d376fecb6274aa46ff1037cf7ae90da6","tid":1846021,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T12:44:39.000Z","msg":"香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/